Latika has demonstrated a strong commitment to the Firm’s compliance, risk management, and control standards. She applies meticulous attention to testing and verification, ensuring her work is thoroughly validated through comprehensive end-to-end and component-level test cases. Her proactive approach was especially valuable during the T+1 migration, where she identified and raised deployment concerns in advance to ensure a smooth transition.

Her colleagues commend her ability to anticipate long-term impacts and her proactive communication with downstream users, alerting them to potential risks. Latika’s dedication to operational stability is evident in her commitment during production outages, as she consistently remains engaged until issues are fully resolved. Her active participation in team discussions and code reviews, combined with her thoughtful feedback and problem-solving abilities, underscores her role as a key contributor to the team’s risk management and compliance efforts.
